# Project Structure

The project follows this directory structure:

```
city_livability_project/
│
├── data/
│   ├── raw/                    # Raw data
│   ├── processed/              # Processed data
│   └── final/                  # Final data and visualizations
│
├── src/                        # Source code
│   ├── data_collection.py      # Data collection from APIs
│   ├── data_processing.py      # Data cleaning and processing
│   ├── scoring_algorithm.py    # Livability score calculation
│   ├── visualization.py        # Graphs and visualizations
│   ├── education_data_collection.py # Education data collection
│   └── health_data_collection.py    # Health data collection
│
├── notebooks/                  # Jupyter notebooks
│   ├── 01_data_exploration.ipynb
│   ├── 02_analysis.ipynb
│   └── 03_final_report.ipynb
│
├── config/
│   └── api_keys.py            # API keys configuration
│
├── requirements.txt           # Python packages
└── README.md                 # Project description
```

The main workflow follows these steps:
1. Data collection from multiple APIs
2. Data processing and cleaning
3. Score calculation using weighted metrics
4. Visualization and final analysis